"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:36:39.000Z","msg":"Tai Yiu Ting, 戴耀廷<br />\n11月17日 14:14 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n民主派區選聯盟共推薦了397名候選人，佔452個選區的88%。<br />\n<br />\n有五個區議會選區（灣仔、南區、油尖旺、荃灣、離島）的候選人100%得推薦，八個區議會（中西區、九龍城、黃大仙、觀塘、屯門、元朗、大埔、葵青）有超過九成候選人得推薦，兩個區議會（東區、深水埗）有八成多候選人得推薦。<br />\n<br />\n這名單是選民非常重要的參考。<br />\n<br />\n餘下在沙田、西貢及北區這三區也有不少候選人得推薦（56-78%）。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">在這三區，大家還可參考地區民主派組織是否支持，如沙田的沙田區政及西貢的將軍澳民生關注組。</span><br />\n<br />\n以今屆那麼多人參選，能做到不算太多撞區，已是各方努力的極大成果。希望在下屆能做到零撞區及百分百推薦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/74352575_2649520358439876_1992352083558268928_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQkPnjQKTfnAWStEJEiIRGlSiZq7LAWqg_vOaK0w3yYjt14ssist_85I9TxPIxTGGcE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-2.xx&amp;oh=e6bde0357e1494fd41049037d5fd9f5c&amp;oe=5E7DF657\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F74352575_2649520358439876_1992352083558268928_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_oc%3DAQkPnjQKTfnAWStEJEiIRGlSiZq7LAWqg_vOaK0w3yYjt14ssist_85I9TxPIxTGGcE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sin2-2.xx%26oh%3De6bde0357e1494fd41049037d5fd9f5c%26oe%3D5E7DF657&h=e01a43e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/BennyTaiHK/posts/?ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FBennyTaiHK%2Fposts%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=0aad9d33\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/BennyTaiHK/posts/?ref=page_internal</a>"},{"pid":"9102d18790b376a73e6bef6f84f9bdeff5ea21ce","tid":1745731,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:27:03.000Z","msg":"Tai Yiu Ting, 戴耀廷<br />\n11月17日 14:14 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n民主派區選聯盟共推薦了397名候選人，佔452個選區的88%。<br />\n<br />\n有五個區議會選區（灣仔、南區、油尖旺、荃灣、離島）的候選人100%得推薦，八個區議會（中西區、九龍城、黃大仙、觀塘、屯門、元朗、大埔、葵青）有超過九成候選人得推薦，兩個區議會（東區、深水埗）有八成多候選人得推薦。<br />\n<br />\n這名單是選民非常重要的參考。<br />\n<br />\n餘下在沙田、西貢及北區這三區也有不少候選人得推薦（56-78%）。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">在這三區，大家還可參考地區民主派組織是否支持，如沙田的沙田區政及西貢的將軍澳民生關注組。</span><br />\n<br />\n以今屆那麼多人參選，能做到不算太多撞區，已是各方努力的極大成果。希望在下屆能做到零撞區及百分百推薦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/74352575_2649520358439876_1992352083558268928_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQkPnjQKTfnAWStEJEiIRGlSiZq7LAWqg_vOaK0w3yYjt14ssist_85I9TxPIxTGGcE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-2.xx&amp;oh=e6bde0357e1494fd41049037d5fd9f5c&amp;oe=5E7DF657\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F74352575_2649520358439876_1992352083558268928_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_oc%3DAQkPnjQKTfnAWStEJEiIRGlSiZq7LAWqg_vOaK0w3yYjt14ssist_85I9TxPIxTGGcE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sin2-2.xx%26oh%3De6bde0357e1494fd41049037d5fd9f5c%26oe%3D5E7DF657&h=e01a43e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/BennyTaiHK/posts/?ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FBennyTaiHK%2Fposts%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=0aad9d33\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/BennyTaiHK/posts/?ref=page_internal</a>"},{"pid":"e8f01be7f1bd749e4ade323e37cbbaaab7f7f51d","tid":1745731,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"agree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}